window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Countless Joyful Dawns</b></p> <p>Elaine, Iona, Auri, and Fenrir enjoy life as the years and centuries roll by.</p> <p>Their idyllic lifestyle is shattered when Erebus, the planetoid sent by the mad lich Thanwa Temirak, arrives on an intercept course to Pallos. Gods, Dragons, and every Classer on Pallos must work together to save the entire world.</p> <p>And as Iona levels, the spectre of a showdown between the Paladin and Lun'Kat rises. It is time to complete the divine quest that Selene and Lunaris have assigned her.</p> <p>It is time to free the moons.</p>"; 
